    "name-poly": "from Greek polys: many, much, or more than one.",
    "name-puff": "a soft breath or little cloud, a nod to learning online in the cloud.",
    "name-sub": "Poly comes from the Greek polys, meaning many. Puff suggests a small, soft cloud, like an internet cloud for language practice. Together, Poly-Puff means many languages and ideas gathered in one light place to learn.",
    "name-tag": "The name",
