    "cookies-clarity-text": "(provided by Microsoft Corporation) - captures anonymised session recordings, heatmaps, and interaction data to help us improve usability. Clarity masks sensitive content by default. Microsoft's privacy policy:",
    "cookies-eea-label": "For users in the European Economic Area (EEA) and South Africa:",
    "cookies-eea-text": "Analytics cookies are only activated after you provide explicit consent, in accordance with the GDPR and POPIA.",
    "cookies-ga-text": "(provided by Google LLC) - collects anonymised usage data such as pages visited, time on site, and referring sources. Google may transfer this data to servers in the United States. Google's privacy policy:",
    "cookies-h2": "10. Cookies & Analytics",
    "cookies-intro": "Our website uses cookies and similar tracking technologies. Here is what we use and why:",
    "cookies-noadvert": "We do not use advertising cookies or sell any data to third parties.",
    "cookies-strictly-label": "Strictly Necessary Cookies:",
    "cookies-strictly-text": "These keep the website functioning (e.g., keeping you logged in). They cannot be disabled.",
