    "my-progress": "Inqubekela phambili yami",
    "name-poly": "kusuka kwelesiGrikhi polys: okuningi noma okungaphezu kokukodwa.",
    "name-puff": "umphefumulo othambile noma ifu elincane, inkomba yokufunda online ku-cloud.",
    "name-sub": "U-Poly uvela egameni lesiGrikhi elithi polys, okusho okuningi. U-Puff ukhumbuza ifu elincane nelithambile, njengama-cloud e-inthanethi okuzijwayeza ulimi. Ndawonye, u-Poly-Puff usho izilimi nemibono eminingi endaweni elula yokufunda.",
    "name-tag": "Igama",
