    "ob-btn-next": "Okulandelayo →",
    "ob-btn-prev": "← Emuva",
    "ob-btn-skip": "Yeqa umzungangezi",
    "ob-s1-body": "Usanda dala i-akhawunti yakho. Lo mzungangezi omfushane uzokubonisa ukuthi yonke into ikuphi nokuthi ungawusebenzisa kanjani kahle uhlelo lwakho lokufunda.",
    "ob-s1-title": "Wamukelekile ku-Poly-Puff! 🎉",
    "ob-s2-body": "Ngaphambi kokuthi uqale ukuzijwayeza, thatha imizuzu eyi-2 ukugcwalisa iphrofayili yakho. Engeza ulimi lwakho lwendabuko, izinga lesiNgisi, umsebenzi nezinhloso zokufunda. I-AI isebenzisa lokhu ukuze <strong style=\"color:#56f0c0\">yenze wonke umsebenzi ukuba ngowakho</strong>--ukwenza ukuzijwayeza kube kusebenza kakhudlwana.",
    "ob-s2-cta": "→ Iya ephrofayilini",
    "ob-s2-skip": "Ngizokwenza ngemuva",
    "ob-s2-title": "Kuqala: Gcwalisa iphrofayili yakho 👤",
    "ob-s3-body": "Leli khasi liyisikhungo sakho. Yonke imojuli yokuzijwayeza ilula ukufinyelela--Umdali Wokuhumusha, Uhlelo Lolimi, Isilulumagama, Ukulalela, Ukubhala nokunye. Yibhukhmakhi ukuze uhlale ungatholakala.",
    "ob-s3-title": "Isikhungo sakho sokufunda 🏠",
    "ob-s4-body": "Umdali Wokuhumusha iyimojuli eyinhloko. I-AI ikunika umusho ngolimi lwakho ukuba uwuhumush ube isiNgisi, bese uthola <strong style=\"color:#7ee8fa\">impendulo eningiliziwe yohlelo lolimi namagama</strong>. Isebenza kuwo wonke amazinga, kusuka ku-A1 kuya ku-C2.",
    "ob-s4-title": "Qala lapha: Umdali Wokuhumusha ↔",
    "ob-s5-body": "Hlola isuite ephelele: <strong>Ukuzijwayeza Uhlelo Lolimi</strong>, <strong>Amaqoqo Amagama</strong>, amakaridhi e-<strong>Silulumagama</strong>, <strong>Ukulalela</strong> no-<strong>Ukubhala</strong>. Yonke imojuli isebenzisa impendulo ye-AI ehlela iphrofayili yakho nezinga lakho.",
    "ob-s5-title": "Amamojuli Okuzijwayeza 📚",
    "ob-s6-body": "Landelela amanqolobane akho nezintambo ku-<strong>Inqubekela Phambili</strong>. I-<strong>Nselelo Yosuku</strong> igcina intambo yakho iqhubeka--ukuqhubekeka kuyindlela eisheshayo ekukhulumeni ngokutekelela. Ukuhlela izivivinyo ze-<strong>IELTS</strong>, ze-<strong>TOEFL</strong> neze-<strong>CAE</strong> nakho kulokhu.",
    "ob-s6-title": "Inqubekela Phambili & Inselelo Yosuku 📊",
    "ob-s7-body": "Qala ngokugcwalisa iphrofayili yakho, bese ufinyelela ku-Umdali Wokuhumusha. Njengoba uzijwayeza kakhulu, kakhulu konke kuba ngokwakho. Nhlanhla!",
    "ob-s7-practice": "Qala Ukuzijwayeza",
