    "ob-btn-prev": "← Kutiychiy",
    "ob-btn-skip": "Puriy saruchiy",
    "ob-s1-body": "Kunanmi cuentaykita ruwanki. Kay pisi puriy suyukunata rikuchinki maypin tukuy ima kasqanta, imaynatan yachay kawsaymantam aswanta tariyta atinkichu.",
    "ob-s1-title": "Poly-Puff-pi allin shamunaykipi! 🎉",
    "ob-s2-body": "Yachay qallarinman ñawpaqta, 2 minutota tiyay perfilnikipi. Mama simiykita, inglés yachayniykita, llamk’ayniykita, chaymantam yachay munaynikikunata yapay. AI kayta <strong style=\"color:#56f0c0\">sapa yachay ruwanata riqsichipunapaq</strong> llamk’achin - yachay aswam allin kachun.",
    "ob-s2-cta": "→ Perfilman riy",
    "ob-s2-skip": "Qhipanpi ruwayman",
    "ob-s2-title": "Ñawpaqta: Perfil Ruwanaykita Tukuchinki 👤",
    "ob-s3-body": "Kay qhipa paginam wasinki. Sapa yachay modulom huk clic karunchallapi - Translation Trainer, Gramatika, Simikuna, Uyariy, Qillqay, chaymantapas. Bookmarkpi churay wiñaypipim kutimunankipaq.",
    "ob-s3-title": "Yachay Wasinki 🏠",
    "ob-s4-body": "Translation Trainer ñawpaq modulom. AI simiykipi rimayta qusunki ingléspi tikranaykipaq, chaymantam <strong style=\"color:#7ee8fa\">gramatika chaymantam simi willaykuyta chikan-chikanpi</strong> qusunki. Tukuy yachay patamanmi ruran, A1-manta C2-kama.",
    "ob-s4-title": "Kaypin Qallay: Translation Trainer ↔",
    "ob-s5-body": "Tukuy hunt’ayta maskay: <strong>Gramatika Yachay</strong>, <strong>Word Chunks</strong>, <strong>Simikuna</strong> kartakuna, <strong>Uyariy</strong>, chaymantam <strong>Qillqay</strong>. Sapa modulom AI willaykuyta perfilniykiman yachay patamanmi riqsichin.",
    "ob-s5-title": "Aswan Yachay Modulokuna 📚",
    "ob-s6-body": "Puntuniykikunata, churanakuyniykikunata, chaymantam allinyanata <strong>Ñawpaqman Riy</strong>pi qhaway. <strong>Sapa Punchaw Sasachakuy</strong> churanakuyniykita waqaychan - sapa punchaw ruwayam usqhayllata rimayta yanapan. <strong>IELTS</strong>, <strong>TOEFL</strong>, chaymantam <strong>CAE</strong> examenkunapaqpas wakichiy tarikun.",
    "ob-s6-title": "Ñawpaqman Riy & Sapa Punchaw Sasachakuy 📊",
    "ob-s7-body": "Perfilnikipi tukuchinawan qallay, chaymantam Translation Trainer-pi yaykuy. Aswam yachakunkiqa, tukuymi aswam riqsisuyki. Allin suerte!",
